title: Passenger vehicles stay ahead of the curve for 2nd month in calendar year
description: It would be the first time in seven years when February will see two consecutive years of growth on YoY basis. In the first 10 months of FY24, passenger car makers sold 3.46 million vehicles, up 7.8% year-on-year.
